  ShadowDensity: 1.000000
  Text: |-
    Make sure you use you assign your own 
    RenderTarget to ImageVirtContent. Swap the current one! 
    
    This asset will allow you to compose a texture that renders 
    virtual content and background content together. 
    
    A confirmation of this will be seeing an "infinite mirror" 
    effect in the composite texture 
    
    Keep this texture turned off in your application, this is just a reference for you to understand how to obtained a composed image (virtual content and background together) 
